      "text": "I don't talk about the weather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I worked there in Courtaulds, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was interesting, the [INAUDIBLE] [? economist, ?] they was very, very nice people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took me with 58 years in the private pension scheme.",
